s. do you have some reason to think not? o~~* /_) ' / / /_/ ' , , ' ,_ _ \|/ - ~ -~~~~~~~~~~~/_) / / / / / / (_) (_) / / / _\~~~~~~~~~~~zap! / \ (_) (_) / | \ | | bill higgins fermi national accelerator laboratory \ / bitnet: higgins@fnal.bitnet - - internet: higgins@fnal.fnal.gov ~ span/hepnet: 43011::higgins
