rs invested in its development. george krumins -- pufferfish observatory |^^^^^\^^^^| the universe had its origin gfk39017@uxa.cso.uiuc.edu ^^^/\ \^^^ in two hockeysticks colliding / /\ \ "home of the hockeystick /_/ \_\ memorial telescope"
